Pengo Industries Inc said ithas agreed to sell its Wireline Products Manufacturing Divisionin Fort Worth, Texas, Wireline Services Division operations inseveral locations and Pengo International Inc subsidiary toJohn Wood Group PLC for undisclosed terms.    The company said the Wireline Services operations beingsold are in Lafayette, Houma and Harvey, La., Alvin, Odessa andLongview, Texas, and Moore, Okla.    Pengo said its Kuykenball Slickline operation in Moore andsurplus wireline equipment operations in fort Worth andCleburne, Texas, will be sold separately. Reuter&#3;